                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12733891" author="fpj" created="Wed, 22 Jul 2009 00:20:29 +0100"  >&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Adds a case to leader election to recover from a lost message when one single follower elects a leader, but the leader missed the new vote from the follower. This is not a really critical case because in practice the servers would just move to a new round of leader election, and the likelihood that this keeps happening forever is small;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It adds a unit test that basically mocks a server to force a particular sequence and interleaving of messages;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It makes some methods and variables public in QuorumCnxManager to enable the unit test to access them directly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
